            How does the web application work?
            </dt>

                    <dd class = "col-sm-10">
                        Input from user is passed as instance of StringStatistic class. 
                        User is able to choose between analysis shown in graphs or in text. 
                        If the user doesn't want to insert their own text button for default string can be used.
                        User cannot pass an empty string. 
                        If the string is only spaces and other white spaces, 
                        an exception is called and warning page is shown.
